com.siperian.sif.message

Class BvtField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.Parameter
      • com.siperian.sif.message.Field
        • com.siperian.sif.message.BvtField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class BvtField
extends Field
    This class represents a base object column that is trust-enabled and includes the rowid of the base object record contributing to the value based on the BVT calculation.

    See Also:
    Field, GetBvtResponse.getRecord(), Serialized Form
